    "description": "<strong>我们希望有更多热爱这类型游戏的朋友们可以参与到试玩并给出任何游戏反馈，大家的支持是开发者的最大动力！感谢！<br>《魔幻砖域》交流QQ群：757592376</strong><br><br><strong>版本包含部分卡牌和第一章的内容</strong><br><br><strong>欢迎来到魔幻砖域！作为初来乍到的冒险者，你需要通过砖块对决来战胜这里各种魔物敌人。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/a578096a56182518f2f4d28c7dc39ebb.avif?t=1729753444\" width=615 height=72 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/5ca0c8228b1b75f78da874728548cda0.poster.avif?t=1729753444\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/5ca0c8228b1b75f78da874728548cda0.webm?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/5ca0c8228b1b75f78da874728548cda0.mp4?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>在单局中，敌人和你会在回合内依次将魔物砖块打出在棋盘上。小心选择你的策略，尝试占有更多的地块以获得更多的分数。游戏结束时分数更高的一方将获得胜利！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/7a88124969ea1d18ccb44ac84bb8cf7e.avif?t=1729753444\" width=615 height=72 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/7fb078ed2a997788a2ba05d90be0032f.poster.avif?t=1729753444\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/7fb078ed2a997788a2ba05d90be0032f.webm?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/7fb078ed2a997788a2ba05d90be0032f.mp4?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>魔物砖块是战斗中的主要单位，他们有着不同的形象，体型和技能，有时他们还会产生数量不同的奥法砖块作为自己影响力的延续，帮助你占领更多的地块。<br>但是需要注意的是奥法砖块往往更脆弱，你需要更加谨慎的选择摆放他们。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/62f0722b88afd1306780217e9bc8cf23.avif?t=1729753444\" width=615 height=72 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/5519c53b70dd10b0d6307441f2851dbb.poster.avif?t=1729753444\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/5519c53b70dd10b0d6307441f2851dbb.webm?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/5519c53b70dd10b0d6307441f2851dbb.mp4?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>单局中有可能会出现各种各样的地形，学会利用这些优势地形，或者远离糟糕的地形。究竟这些地形会让你的计划事半功倍还是一团乱麻呢？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/912ef586b524dd9eed289ebfb43ce724.avif?t=1729753444\" width=615 height=72 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/3bba463fa95458be96f4d30e3de1c5ff.poster.avif?t=1729753444\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/3bba463fa95458be96f4d30e3de1c5ff.webm?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/3bba463fa95458be96f4d30e3de1c5ff.mp4?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>战胜对手，解开谜题后都可以选择新的卡牌。选择路线来规避风险或者挑战强敌。尝试构筑不同风格的卡组，完善你的卡牌收集。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/606b710df2f73b225510956ed03de92b.poster.avif?t=1729753444\" width=120 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/606b710df2f73b225510956ed03de92b.webm?t=1729753444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/15e014898a154c53a608ced0b2bbe109.apng?t=1729753444\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243920/extras/15e014898a154c53a608ced0b2bbe109.poster.avif?t=1729753444\" class=\"bb_img\" width=120 height=120 /></picture></span>",
